Paper: hep-th/0005216

Date: 2000-05-24

Title: p-Adic and Adelic Free Relativistic Particle

Authors: G.S.Djordjevic, B.Dragovich and LJ. Nesic

Comments: 9 pages

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A14 (1999) 317-325

We consider spectral problem for a free relativistic particle in p-adic andadelic quantum mechanics. In particular, we found p-adic and adeliceigenfunctions. Within adelic approach there exist quantum states that exhibitdiscrete structure of spacetime at the Planck scale.